tid":1438101,"uid":51952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:51:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6290fb75ce899781defd010826b1a0041d8682d","tid":1438101,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"聽日理撚得你去大埔定機場 <br />\n去大埔嘅自己小心 記住<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地要睇嘅得呢一句：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙大爆炸都唔撚割！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2bec403ec6a35cb8cdb4ae297f3143bfc2bdd3","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45e19f910dc70b54d207b1a8aed689a0ef7e81d5","tid":1438101,"uid":49781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"我走咗啦，btw  可唔可以唔好再標籤和理非或勇武，大家都係手足<br />\n<br />\n[警世] 去機場一轉，點解連登又有人搞分化帶風向？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"更正 係和你飛手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係想講今次嚟咗機場嘅手足 <br />\n手足本無和理非勇武之分<br />\n知唔少前線都有嚟機場join和你飛"},{"pid":"0e18ee420ec8a066e36a875c769b6194f2ec901a","tid":1438101,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9243b0b0ea3ffdbbadcea4de4e1c15e59e4413b4","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">tldr懶人包</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1）口號</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英文為主，現場airdrop口號列表，重複完第一句再嗌第二句<br />\n2）文宣<br />\n按各國語言分區，標示得明顯啲；示威日期地點資訊；放映會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日晏晝去咗機場，大家都辛苦喇，以下係我個人少少意見，希望可以一齊做得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（好少出post，如果排版排得唔好講定sorry先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">口號</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講英文</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我今日聽到十句口號有四句係香港人加油，兩句係光復香港時代革命，兩句係free hk democracy now，淨低係do you hear the people sing同埋香港警察知法犯法。<br />\n<br />\n如果係市區遊行我覺得嗌廣東話冇問題<br />\n但如果係喺機場向遊客宣傳，我覺得口號以英文為主會好啲，人聽到自己唔識嘅語言係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽唔入耳</span>㗎！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">口號要有列表</span></span><br />\n承上，唔知係咪大家唔熟悉所以唔嗌英文，例如do you hear the people sing大家都係最熟頭兩句，之後就愈唱愈細聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以要有好似陸運會咁嘅口號牌，當然啦我地人多，現場見到有女仔舉牌俾大家跟住唱，但啲字太幼離遠係睇唔到嘅。所以可以喺手機上面打定note，喺現場airdrop俾大家，大家可以跟住嚟嗌，例如咁：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4U5JeZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4U5JeZ.png&h=3b6ca476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重複一次第一句再嗌第二句</span></span><br />\n現場聽到嘅通常係咁：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">光復香港</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港人</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">加油</span><br />\n行過唔知咩事嘅人淨係聽到時代革命同加油<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣應該會好啲：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">領：光復香港</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">眾：光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">領：時代革命</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">眾：時代革命</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">按語言分區</span></span><br />\n最好就可以大大隻字標明你識講嘅同你手持嘅文宣係咩語言，好似遊客區小冊子嘅擺放方式咁，分好中文（繁簡）英文韓文日文西班牙文俾遊客，人地想攞嚟睇都知問邊個攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊客想睇咩？</span></span><br />\n出面見到個post，大概係講遊客會想知邊區將會有示威，無論佢係想去睇睇定想避開，我覺得我地咁樣提醒佢都會賺到印象分！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放映會</span></span><br />\n人天生會想望郁緊嘅嘢，有片有真相，機場放映會真係諗得過㗎！各國youtuber都有整片，以上都可以mark翻係咩語言，方便遊客follow。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日就係和理飛第二日，希望可以集思廣益點樣令到遊客文宣更effective</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日。五。罷買救港</span></span></strong><br />\n罷買運動正式開始<br />\n之前推過罷買,反應唔錯,於是同其他巴打一齊統一搞左星期五,日罷買, 一星期2日, 請幫手集中推以下2個POST<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXM0w4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXM0w4O.jpg&h=6004208b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(和理非全面升級)星期五，日0消費！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436038/page/1</a><br />\n「驚就唔好出街！」BYE BUY DAY 全城罷買投票結果出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436025/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436025/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fdd97c0b38b2cd9c1756751fb4c16a1e6b10e3b9","tid":1438101,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2bec403ec6a35cb8cdb4ae297f3143bfc2bdd3","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45e19f910dc70b54d207b1a8aed689a0ef7e81d5","tid":1438101,"uid":49781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"我走咗啦，btw  可唔可以唔好再標籤和理非或勇武，大家都係手足<br />\n<br />\n[警世] 去機場一轉，點解連登又有人搞分化帶風向？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"更正 係和你飛手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係想講今次嚟咗機場嘅手足 <br />\n手足本無和理非勇武之分<br />\n知唔少前線都有嚟機場join和你飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"啱，呢套講法真係大肆宣傳先得，成日分開和理非同勇武做咩啫"},{"pid":"4228ff25bfb7ff138d79533d0d1ce80521c9f5b7","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"推到機場手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e362bfddab8227dfa3359b399281cc10f81460fc","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea8d3202510b4076ab89185d188b3433620870fb","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e03719bf54c5b46e4bc5cb259f3517a65292b835","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4d90dd9abaa3ea8ed9cbc3c5296ac22b8fab3523","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3fc163d4f282e7167ac3f26a866dde76f3244fea","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d47f7299980e323240d805214e24433fe31ee7a5","tid":1438101,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8f5b529d4